ph.com.globelabs.api.response

Class AccessTokenResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • ph.com.globelabs.api.response.Response
      • ph.com.globelabs.api.response.AccessTokenResponse

  • public class AccessTokenResponse
extends Response
    This object is created from the expected response of the server. Obtainable information include the following: accessToken, subscriberNumber, and error (if any). This response also has a responseCode, responseMessage, and holds the raw HttpResponse. See Response.
